# skills/ 目录全部是内置技能，需要被 git 完整跟踪。
# 用户通过技能市场安装的技能存放在 ~/.openakita/workspaces/default/skills/，
# 不在仓库目录内，无需 ignore。

# Plugins (keep structure)
# Only the two first-class plugins live in plugins/. Everything else has been
